outputs.output_descr:
1. Institutional arrangement established and functional to deliberate and guide the project direction;
2. Civil Society Organisation (CSO) resource centres established and functional to serve a learning hub for CSOs in NAD and Nias;
3. Local Non Governmental Organisations (NGOs) and Community Based Organisations (CBOs) have adequate community development competencies particularly in the areas of rehabilitation and reconstruction monitoring, project management, strategic planning, leadership, and gender related issues;
4. NGOs and CBOs provide written reconstruction monitoring inputs and recommendations;
5. NGOs and CBOs are able to implement small grants programme.
